'''Oliver Maguire''' (died [[January 10]], [[2012]]) played [[Cabbel/Legends|Cabbel]] in [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''The Empire Strikes Back'']].
Outside ''Star Wars'', Maguire has appeared in the long running science fiction series [[Wikipedia:Doctor Who|''Doctor Who'']] where he played a Shrieve in the 1978 story [[Wikipedia:The Ribos Operation|''The Ribos Operation'']] starring [[Tom Baker]].

